Name: Hentai Space
About the game: Hentai Space is a totally classic puzzle game but with a wonderful space atmosphere and a slight Japanese touch ... To solve space puzzles, simply move the pieces that are in disorder and restore order to reform the image. Features: ■ 25 levels! ■ Nice background music! ■ Atmosphere and animated spatial backgrounds! ■ Beautiful Artworks!
